A group under the aegis of Peace Development Security and Humanitarian Rights Association of Niger Deltans has commended the laudable effort of the developmental strides of Governor Ifeanyi Okowa of Delta State. According to the group, Governor Okowa use the instrumentality of the SMART Agenda and the Stronger Delta Vision to position the state on the true path of economic progress. The Group in an open letter appreciated Governor Okowa’s Political sagacity and his quest to develop Delta State across the board. The group, however, added that his unquenchable desire and determination as a detribalised leader,is the drive which made him record the achievements over the years that earned him the sobriquet of “Road Master” and “EKWUEME” of the Universe.